# 🛒 ShopVault - Premium Online Marketplace

![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/status-active-success)
![HTML5](https://img.shields.io/badge/HTML5-E34F26?logo=html5&logoColor=white)
![CSS3](https://img.shields.io/badge/CSS3-1572B6?logo=css3&logoColor=white)
![JavaScript](https://img.shields.io/badge/JavaScript-F7DF1E?logo=javascript&logoColor=black)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue)

> A fully functional e-commerce marketplace built with vanilla HTML, CSS & JavaScript — ideal for internship projects and portfolio demos.

---

## 📸 Preview

![ShopVault Banner](https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498049794561-7780e7231661?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop)

---

## ✨ Features

- **16 Products** across 8 categories
- **Category Filtering** via navbar, cards, and hero buttons
- **Search** with real-time results
- **Sorting** by price, rating, and discount
- **Shopping Cart** with add/remove and quantity tracking
- **Wishlist** with toggle functionality
- **Responsive Design** for mobile, tablet, and desktop
- **Cart Sidebar** with slide-in panel
- **Toast Notifications** for user actions
- **Load More** pagination

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Technology | Purpose |
|------------|---------|
| HTML5 | Structure |
| CSS3 | Styling, animations, responsive design |
| JavaScript (ES6+) | DOM manipulation, state management |
| Font Awesome 6 | Icons |
| Google Fonts | Typography |
| Unsplash | Images |

**Zero dependencies — no frameworks or build tools.**

---

## 📁 Project Structure
shopvault/
├── index.html # Main HTML
├── style.css # Stylesheet
├── script.js # Functionality
└── README.md # Documentation

text

---

## 🚀 Quick Start

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/shopvault.git

# Navigate to folder
cd shopvault

# Open in browser
open index.html
Or deploy directly to GitHub Pages:

Settings → Pages

Select main branch

Save

📱 Responsive Breakpoints
Device	Width	Layout
Desktop	1024px+	Full layout
Tablet	768px	Stacked sections
Mobile	480px	Single column, hamburger menu
⚙️ Core Functionality
javascript
getFilteredProducts()   // Filter & sort products
renderProducts()        // Render to DOM
addToCart(id)           // Add item to cart
removeFromCart(id)      // Remove from cart
toggleWishlist(id)      // Toggle wishlist
showNotification(msg)   // Toast messages
🎨 Design System
Element	Value
Primary	#4f46e5
Accent	#f59e0b
Font	Inter + Poppins
Shadows	sm / md / lg / xl
Radius	6px - 20px
📊 Product Categories
Electronics · Fashion · Home & Garden · Sports · Gaming · Motors · Jewelry · Books

🔮 Roadmap
LocalStorage persistence

Product detail pages

User authentication

Backend API integration

Dark mode

